- User creates a poll
    - Route: /
    - Component: Poll Form
    - Links:
    - Redirects:
        - After creating - /poll/:code

- User lists his polls
    - Route: /poll
    - Component: Poll List
    - Links: /poll/:code
    - Redirects:

- User votes on a poll
    - Route: /poll/:code
    - Component: Poll View
    - Links:
        - /poll/:code/result
        - If user is owner: /poll/:code/edit
    - Redirects: 
        - After voting - /poll/:code/result

- User changes his vote
    - Route: /poll/:code
    - Component: Poll View
    - Links: 
    - Redirects: 
        - After changing the vote - /poll/:code/result

- User edits a poll
    - Route: /poll/:code/edit
    - Component: Poll Form
    - Links: 
    - Redirects: 
        - After editing - /poll/:code

- User creates an account
    - Route: /register
    - Component: User Registration
    - Links: 
    - Redirects: 
        - After registration - /poll

- User makes login
    - Route: /login
    - Component: User Login
    - Links: 
    - Redirects: 
        - After login - /poll
